{"tid":1021443,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"求戒煙方法/心得","createTime":"2019-02-14T09:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T23:25:22.000Z","uid":46807,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"03bb66b487f1ab9b160d1be6ad2a7d3e6ec208a0","tid":1021443,"uid":46807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:04:13.000Z","msg":"Hi 咁多位ching.<br />\n細佬由於前排失戀太傷心以致不幸染上煙癮.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現已後悔莫及.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想趁年輕快快手戒左佢.<br />\n<br />\n煙齡: 半年<br />\n基本上一諗起個ex就想落街食番支煙.<br />\n但去到後期有時做野做到好悶都會想落街食煙.<br />\n<br />\n頭果4個月基本上一日一包.<br />\n呢兩個好d, 一日半一包.<br />\n<br />\n由於發覺自己唔再值得為左個唔好既人而糟蹋自己.<br />\n所以想戒煙.<br />\n想請問咁多位成功戒煙既ching有咩方法/心得可以有效戒除煙癮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 唔是火車頭, 通常都會企係垃圾桶格離食.<br />\n因為我個人本身就係一件垃圾, 物以類聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af9d121ebd95a527006556462e818805bae5de0","tid":1021443,"uid":170867,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:06:07.000Z","msg":"1. 下定決心，做好準備<br />\n訂下戒煙日期<br />\n檢討你以往戒煙的經驗，找出你認為可行或不可行的戒煙方法<br />\n<br />\n2. 爭取支持，宣佈戒煙<br />\n告訴親友你正在戒煙，爭取他們的支持<br />\n致電戒煙熱線，參加戒煙輔導服務<br />\n<br />\n3. 認清令你吸煙的高危情況<br />\n了解你以往吸煙的習慣（例如你通常在何時、何地、與何人、甚麼情況、感覺或思想下吸煙呢？）<br />\n<br />\n4. 清除戒煙障礙，作出改變<br />\n<br />\n如果你希望獲取更多有關戒煙藥物的資訊，請致電東華三院戒煙熱線2332 8977查詢，或與你的家庭醫生或藥劑師聯絡。"},{"pid":"b2cc1c7320303e7bed5195b310a7d9057db40c85","tid":1021443,"uid":154872,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:11:02.000Z","msg":"直接唔食就唔食<br />\n<br />\n點解會有癮？"},{"pid":"a9216c3b0b6431e2bcd92383ded650aa22f5cdc3","tid":1021443,"uid":236401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:12:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b6f2853fbf01db83f0f855b78aca09a301d4a88","tid":1021443,"uid":46807,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b2cc1c7320303e7bed5195b310a7d9057db40c85","tid":1021443,"uid":154872,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:11:02.000Z","msg":"直接唔食就唔食<br />\n<br />\n點解會有癮？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:15:25.000Z","msg":"唔係咁易架葉師傅..."},{"pid":"8ca7cf00440bfa22dabb14aff87d80a0c5de76c5","tid":1021443,"uid":46807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1af9d121ebd95a527006556462e818805bae5de0","tid":1021443,"uid":170867,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:06:07.000Z","msg":"1. 下定決心，做好準備<br />\n訂下戒煙日期<br />\n檢討你以往戒煙的經驗，找出你認為可行或不可行的戒煙方法<br />\n<br />\n2. 爭取支持，宣佈戒煙<br />\n告訴親友你正在戒煙，爭取他們的支持<br />\n致電戒煙熱線，參加戒煙輔導服務<br />\n<br />\n3. 認清令你吸煙的高危情況<br />\n了解你以往吸煙的習慣（例如你通常在何時、何地、與何人、甚麼情況、感覺或思想下吸煙呢？）<br />\n<br />\n4. 清除戒煙障礙，作出改變<br />\n<br />\n如果你希望獲取更多有關戒煙藥物的資訊，請致電東華三院戒煙熱線2332 8977查詢，或與你的家庭醫生或藥劑師聯絡。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:16:52.000Z","msg":"1. 日日都下定決心, 但日日都破戒...<br />\n2. 唔敢比媽媽知我染上煙癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. 已經傷害緊我身體啦, 已有明顯跡象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6e1d556f11183d24482e6d9b51f1910688e63e","tid":1021443,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:17:19.000Z","msg":"食一排加熱煙再戒會容易D, 個癮同傳統煙唔同, 易D甩 (身理上)"},{"pid":"ee4078bab8b57bb32e66e1bedafc8ede5db95eb5","tid":1021443,"uid":46807,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a9216c3b0b6431e2bcd92383ded650aa22f5cdc3","tid":1021443,"uid":236401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:12:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:17:20.000Z","msg":"有冇女介紹黎識?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 183cm高"},{"pid":"66e9eae758bff99b256beff43ec78868f66a39c8","tid":1021443,"uid":61678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:17:45.000Z","msg":"要搵出個trigger先 時間？地點？諗起唔開心回憶想numb pain?"},{"pid":"d0d988fc20f33a017c59361ea17ca2e68baca8a3","tid":1021443,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:18:45.000Z","msg":"唔買煙咪得囉<br />\n身上一支煙都冇&amp;唔問人拎，你煙癮大到想跳樓都冇得吸啦"},{"pid":"54e560a0e515a67952698bd59fe5cac5df4d09ed","tid":1021443,"uid":653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:19:59.000Z","msg":"戒買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只要戒買做事成<br />\n唔好諗住最多1個禮拜1盒咁戒，避免接觸煙友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 盡量搭地鐵減少因等車而空閒時間"},{"pid":"c3ba16a78b44b11e10ad1e107432d3bd8d9a9a09","tid":1021443,"uid":218638,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:22:05.000Z","msg":"食左20年以上 quit了2年幾<br />\n1. 唔好放棄 <br />\n  就算食番一支 第2日一定要成包掉 唔可以再食<br />\n  最緊要記住自己為咩而QUIT<br />\n2. 唔好堆食煙朋友堆<br />\n3. 做運動 <br />\n   每日都要做 易瞓同埋KILL TIME<br />\n4. 唔好比自己有HEA既時間<br />\n  一HEA就去睇書 眼瞓就去瞓<br />\n5. 瞓前最麻煩<br />\n買威士忌飲 飲完瞓<br />\n真係瞓唔到先飲 日日飲快死過食煙<br />\n6. 捱到頭2-3個月 之後先開始難捱<br />\n要避開會令你心煩既野 份工都唔可以令你動氣 有怒火<br />\n<br />\n以上慢慢你就會變番正常人<br />\n之後你聞到煙會自己避開 唔吸氣"},{"pid":"bc0d5814bec2b8e6970c12fff4ca5534b4544e3f","tid":1021443,"uid":78703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:23:57.000Z","msg":"食半年已經一日一包<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91de48fe6a199b35b9c22695f36e51655697d9a","tid":1021443,"uid":236401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:26:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afe55ce30de55b5b3a0549b61c7d8f0be775b11c","tid":1021443,"uid":46807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c91de48fe6a199b35b9c22695f36e51655697d9a","tid":1021443,"uid":236401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:26:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:41:36.000Z","msg":"做乜春"},{"pid":"0c30f726bfdcbe320676f7e8c9bc87f515644872","tid":1021443,"uid":46807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66e9eae758bff99b256beff43ec78868f66a39c8","tid":1021443,"uid":61678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:17:45.000Z","msg":"要搵出個trigger先 時間？地點？諗起唔開心回憶想numb pain?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:41:50.000Z","msg":"Both....."},{"pid":"a48b38495a79671df2d520ff7b341f1fe59e6208","tid":1021443,"uid":46807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0d988fc20f33a017c59361ea17ca2e68baca8a3","tid":1021443,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:18:45.000Z","msg":"唔買煙咪得囉<br />\n身上一支煙都冇&amp;唔問人拎，你煙癮大到想跳樓都冇得吸啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:42:21.000Z","msg":"我試過啦!<br />\n但之後會忍唔住去買....<br />\n週街都係7仔同OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a399c6a1fff266aa1b7b3a91c283f8de678f0e73","tid":1021443,"uid":2239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:44:30.000Z","msg":"我搵東華戒，打去戒煙熱線預約"},{"pid":"37bd05e81e7f1e21525c1ff512b083236744277e","tid":1021443,"uid":166487,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:49:10.000Z","msg":"我介左啦，方法一星期吾落街第二過星期好好多，仲有被開食煙個班人"},{"pid":"96a902adc9d37a279b06be9cb396ee4431cd4fba","tid":1021443,"uid":236401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:53:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0dc94db81092a1159b454db0ab95c378aa928147","tid":1021443,"uid":120850,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:56:10.000Z","msg":"直接斷 <br />\n無訣要<br />\n心境重要d<br />\n第二日想食就諗下第一日咁辛苦都捱到唔好浪費左去<br />\n如此類推"},{"pid":"ff1542af786532fd9be8882e8eae295178666bb3","tid":1021443,"uid":120850,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2b6f2853fbf01db83f0f855b78aca09a301d4a88","tid":1021443,"uid":46807,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b2cc1c